A cyberpunk cityscape at night with towering neon-lit servers acting as buildings, connected by glowing fiber optic cables forming bridges between them. In the foreground, a massive translucent shield barrier surrounds one cluster of servers, with streams of bright data packets flowing through a single fortified gateway checkpoint. The gateway pulses with scanning lasers examining each data stream before allowing passage. Rain falls through holographic advertisements, reflecting off wet streets below. The color palette features deep purples, electric blues, and hot pink accents against dark metallics.
